    "For an explainer to be faithful, the important features of the model should correspond to the important ones of the explainer.",
    "It is measured by perturbing the explainer's features.",
    "For an explainer to be faithful, given a subset size |S|, the change in the predictor b's output between the perturbed explanation and the unchanged one should be proportional to the sum of attribution scores.",
